OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy with a scattering of
OL,6,Fshowers across the north at first,
OL,7,Fthese tending to become lighter and
OL,8,Fisolated into the afternoon. Some
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells at times, with
OL,10,Fwinds gradually easing later.
OL,11,FTemperatures near average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FGenerally dry with some clear
OL,14,Fspells at first, but cloud thickening
OL,15,Ffrom the west towards midnight,
OL,16,Fbringing some patchy rain and drizzle
OL,17,Feastwards through the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
