OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA rather cloudy start, with
OL,6,Fsome patchy light rain or drizzle.
OL,7,FHowever, becoming mostly dry into the
OL,8,Fafternoon with bright intervals
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Feeling noticeably milder
OL,10,Fwith just a gentle breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FWednesday rather cloudy, damp across
OL,14,Fwestern hills, elsewhere drier. Mild.
OL,15,FRain band moving south overnight,
OL,16,FThursday, probably brighter and
OL,17,Fcooler. Friday, variable cloud, patchy
OL,18,Frain easing. Wet and windy later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
